      "role": "user",
      "content": "i was looking at old photos today. i don't even recognize that person anymore. it feels like everything that actually made me \"me\"—the spark, the drive, the soul—just died a long time ago. now i'm just going through the motions. like i'm a ghost inhabiting a body that won't stop moving. it's just so exhausting to keep pretending i'm actually alive.",
